1. *Uđem* u kuću i zapalim svetlo. (I enter the house and turn on the light.)
2. Okrenem se i *uđem* u sobu. (I turn around and enter the room.)
3. Ušla sam unutra i *uđoh* u dnevnu sobu. (I went in and entered the living room.)
4. *Uđoh* u trgovinu da kupim povrće. (I entered the store to buy vegetables.)
5. *Uđem* u lift i stisnem dugme. (I enter the elevator and press the button.)